{"tid":2199151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「港無三權分立」 35%非泛民反對","createTime":"2020-09-12T03:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T05:10:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2b4188150d296a8ce1487e2a090e287b2a0f17","tid":2199151,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/2EE3ZCL3F5E3VOOFXQI4HEQEHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2F2EE3ZCL3F5E3VOOFXQI4HEQEHA%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=281ca2ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2F2EE3ZCL3F5E3VOOFXQI4HEQEHA%2F&h=3b7e47c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/2EE3ZCL3F5E3VOOFXQI4HEQEHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「港無三權分立」 35%非泛民反對<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0M1WETF-chz94VpJhyEgP_GGs_Q=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/76SSPOBSE5FHLBMWB5Q6KND5LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0M1WETF-chz94VpJhyEgP_GGs_Q%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F76SSPOBSE5FHLBMWB5Q6KND5LY.jpg&h=ae746fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁啟智<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥、教育局局長楊潤雄、中聯辦、港澳辦突然聲稱香港沒有三權分立，連撐政府的部份支持者也不能接受。香港民意研究民調顯示，63%人反對「香港從來沒有三權分立」的意見，非民主派支持者中，更有35%反對這個說法。有學者指稱，民調結果反映連支持者政府的人對政府說法也感疑慮，而社會共識是三權互相制衡、司法獨立：「香港幾多人都反對香港冇三權分立嘅睇法」。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所的「我們香港人」計劃本周一至四，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：政府支持者也有疑慮<br />\n<br />\n結果顯示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。「我們香港人」計劃名譽總監梁啟智稱，如果詳細分析非民主派支持者的取態，表示「好反對」政府的說法多達30%，「幾反對」則只有5%，：「反對嘅人係好反對！」他又指，非民主派支持者對香港沒有三權分立論有疑慮，其中一個原因可能是建制派甚至香港政府，都曾經表示香港有三權分立，作為建制派支持者「未必一時間反應過來」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AT43ZlpbqIU7gRRkgaWsaaXC1S0=/835x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2HGQNXLSNHHTGHSGQYXY5CIGU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAT43ZlpbqIU7gRRkgaWsaaXC1S0%3D%2F835x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2HGQNXLSNHHTGHSGQYXY5CIGU.gif&h=118cf46e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32c6158478b2de9ef7ee832cc41efcb6f36d3155","tid":2199151,"uid":297859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"大家要留意<br />\n好多人就算係黃都唔會話自己係民主派支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eff25106eac89746fb6f0e36b472871d1e7e87","tid":2199151,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"洗咩你反對姐，依家我話你冇就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855a4af48294ab85bc56d7c599df7bf9790f9414","tid":2199151,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"犯國安法拉得"},{"pid":"5ebc2e405ca67fec33ee55936fa2845d2417535f","tid":2199151,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5eff25106eac89746fb6f0e36b472871d1e7e87","tid":2199151,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"洗咩你反對姐，依家我話你冇就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班友都痴線"},{"pid":"7dc1e4d58e0203dca5faa2c81f0fdae414c804a7","tid":2199151,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c6158478b2de9ef7ee832cc41efcb6f36d3155","tid":2199151,"uid":297859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"大家要留意<br />\n好多人就算係黃都唔會話自己係民主派支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk